data.description: A must see, warm and inviting prime Santa Monica Townhome.  Boasting three bedrooms and three bathrooms, this two-story charming home is everything you have been looking for.  The kitchen has been completely remodeled with designer touches including porcelain flooring, quartz countertops, stainless appliance package, and laundry room.  Off the kitchen is the large dining space complete with floor to ceiling custom cabinetry.  The living room features hardwood floors, a stunning original stone fireplace, custom wet bar, updated recessed lighting, and a relaxing patio.  Upstairs you enter your light filled primary suite with walk-in closet through double doors where you will experience a spa everyday in your primary bath.  Never lack counter space with custom built oversized Carrara marble vanity, beautiful absolute black granite floors, and extra-large free standing soaking tub.  Luxuriate in the rainfall shower room with three showerheads and Bluetooth sound system.  Two more light filled guest bedrooms are located upstairs.  Two additional baths in the home have been updated with modern marble vanities, floors, and fixtures.  New Central AC with UV light air filter and Nest system. The gated garage features 2 separate assigned parking spaces. Amazing location with close proximity to Douglas Park, Erewhon, Trader Joes, Whole Foods, and many more!
